title: DJ's Pre-Draft Media Call
itunes:title: DJ's Pre-Draft Media Call
description:
Daniel Jeremiah is back with a special new episode. DJ answered questions from the media through a conference call for over two hours last week! Check the best of the call as the NFL Network analyst answers questions regarding the draft, team fits and all the prospects within it. All things NFL draft are covered on the call!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
